heros.name: Superman
heros.power: Flight, superhuman strength, x-ray vision, heat vision, cold breath, super-speed, enhanced hearing, and nigh-invulnerability

heros.name: Thor
heros.power: Control thunder and immunity to most diseases

heros.name: Hulk
heros.power: Immense superhuman strength, speed, stamina, and durability

heros.name: Captain Marvel
heros.power: Enhanced strength, stamina, agility, and durability, as well as flight, and almost total immunity to toxins and poisons.
